                <span class="section-eyebrow">Technical Specifications</span>
                <h2>How Almond SDI Systems Are Designed</h2>
                <p>Almond SDI design must account for tree spacing, root architecture, harvest operations, and long orchard life cycles. Our specifications:</p>
                <ul class="check-list" style="margin-top:20px;">
                    <li>One or two laterals per row depending on tree spacing</li>
                    <li>Installation depth: 12–18 inches (below cultivation depth)</li>
                    <li>Emitter spacing: 18–24 inches along the lateral</li>
                    <li>Flow rates sized to match your soil's infiltration rate</li>
                    <li>Pressure-compensating emitters for sloped terrain</li>
                    <li>Anti-siphon valves at every zone</li>
                    <li>Harvest-compatible routing to avoid equipment conflicts</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
